struct  BspUtils_Ub960Status
 Status of UB960 initialization. When numDetected > 0, indicates UB960 EVM is initialized. When numDetected == 0, indicates UB960 EVM did not detect any sources. Please check the I2C addresses in case a source was connected but not detected. More...
 
struct  BspUtils_Ub960SourceI2cAddr
 Configure I2C address of the sources When numDetected > 0, indicates UB960 EVM is initialized. When numDetected == 0, indicates UB960 EVM did not detect any sources. Please check the I2C addresses in case a source was connected but not detected. More...

Detailed Description

Defines APIs to initialize, de-initialize UB960 EVM, address aliases & reset sensors.
